cs.IT, cs.SP, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.NA. 

The paper deals with compressed sensing (CS) and signal processing, which are covered by the cs.IT and cs.SP categories. The focus on spectral sparsity and recovery of frequency components suggests cs.SI as another likely category. The use of prior information and algorithms also suggests cs.LG as a possible category. Finally, the mention of probability and recovery suggests cs.NA as a potential category.
